headline: Qnity Electronics, Inc. to Join S&P 500 on Nov. 3
summary: WILMINGTON, Del., October 28, 2025--Qnity Electronics, Inc. ("Qnity"), a premier technology solutions leader across the semiconductor value chain, will join the S&P 500 when its stock begins "regular-way" trading on the NYSE on Nov. 3, 2025 under the ticker symbol "Q" following its intended separation from DuPont de Nemours ("DuPont") on Nov. 11 . Qnity’s addition to the S&P 500 recognizes its sustained growth, innovation, and commitment to making tomorrow’s technologies possible.
